    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for checking out my car! I\u2019ve truly enjoyed driving this beauty, and it\u2019s been super reliable for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-looked after, so it's totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner. If you're looking for a dependable ride that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you! Feel free to message me if you want to come by and take a look!",
