    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This FD-generation chassis represents the pinnacle of Japanese sports car engineering, featuring the high-revving 13B-REW rotary engine equipped with its signature sequential twin-turbocharger system. The powertrain delivers smooth, staged boost through the mid-range, managed by a precise five-speed manual gearbox and a Torsen limited-slip differential. Its front-midship engine placement achieves a near-perfect 50/50 weight distribution, while the four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and lightweight aluminum components ensure exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. Mechanically sound with a focus on cooling system integrity and vacuum line maintenance, this example offers a visceral, analog driving experience that remains a benchmark for aerodynamic efficiency and power-to-weight performance.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
