    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that perfectly balances performance with everyday comfort. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only the minor, inevitable stone chips expected of a car that has been genuinely enjoyed and cared for. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple and free of tears, the dashboard is entirely crack-free, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment system to the climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine delivers consistent, smooth power, backed by a comprehensive service history that includes a recent oil change and a full brake inspection. It handles with precision and offers a quiet, responsive ride that makes it ideal for both spirited weekend drives and reliable commuting. This is an honest, dependable car that has been kept in top-tier mechanical shape and is ready for its next chapter.",
